            <span class="blog-category">Social Media</span>
            <span class="blog-card-title">How Florida Small Businesses Can Dominate Social Media in 2026</span>
            <p class="blog-card-excerpt">Most Florida businesses try social media, post for a few weeks, and quit. The problem is never the platform — it's the strategy. Here's what actually works.</p>
            <div class="blog-card-footer">
              <span>March 12, 2026</span>
              <span class="read-more-link">Read more &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/what-is-ai-automation-and-how-it-transforms-small-business/" class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-card-img"><img src="/blog/images/n2hvMUYzyesDvDO4TrpsK_pirj3Eyl.jpg" alt="AI automation dashboard with circuit board technology" width="400" height="180" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="blog-card-body">
            <span class="blog-category">AI Automation</span>
            <span class="blog-card-title">What Is AI Automation and How It Can Transform Your Small Business</span>
            <p class="blog-card-excerpt">AI automation isn't robots replacing your staff — it's software handling the repetitive tasks that drain your time and cost you leads every single day.</p>
            <div class="blog-card-footer">
              <span>March 10, 2026</span>
              <span class="read-more-link">Read more &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/local-seo-guide-florida-small-business/" class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-card-img"><img src="/blog/images/yu7WKtk0fUDgXGX8Kky57_FqhbhiXz.jpg" alt="Aerial view of Florida coastline with Google Maps location pin" width="400" height="180" loading="lazy" /></div>
          <div class="blog-card-body">
            <span class="blog-category">SEO</span>
            <span class="blog-card-title">Local SEO Guide: How Florida Small Businesses Get Found on Google</span>
            <p class="blog-card-excerpt">When someone searches "best contractor near me" or "restaurant in Palm Coast FL" — does your business show up? If not, you're losing customers every day.</p>
            <div class="blog-card-footer">
              <span>March 8, 2026</span>
              <span class="read-more-link">Read more &rarr;</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="wave" style="background:#f5f6fb"><svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M0,60 C480,0 960,0 1440,60 L1440,60 L0,60 Z" fill="#05091a"/></svg></div>

  <section class="mid-cta" aria-label="Newsletter CTA">
    <div class="mid-cta-inner">
      <div>
        <h2>Ready to Grow Your Business?</h2>
        <p>Book a free 30-minute strategy call. We'll review your marketing and show you exactly what's holding your business back.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary btn-large">Book My Free Call &rarr;</a>
    </div>
  </section>

{% endblock %}
